A graphic designer can build
a thriving freelance business

00:18:42.821 --> 00:18:45.281
without ever commuting to an office.

00:18:45.790 --> 00:18:49.301
For people with disabilities
who might face

00:18:49.931 --> 00:18:53.231
physical barriers
in traditional office environments,

00:18:53.380 --> 00:18:56.470
who might experience
discrimination in hiring,

00:18:56.740 --> 00:18:59.500
or who might need
flexible work arrangements,

00:18:59.691 --> 00:19:01.330
the digital economy

00:19:01.950 --> 00:19:03.040
represents

00:19:03.616 --> 00:19:08.019
unprecedented opportunity,
but only if they have the skills

00:19:08.020 --> 00:19:09.020
to access it.

00:19:09.541 --> 00:19:11.861
Here's the economic reality.

00:19:11.891 --> 00:19:17.081
The tech sector is growing faster
than almost any other industry.

00:19:17.381 --> 00:19:20.591
There's a global shortage
of qualified tech workers.

00:19:20.831 --> 00:19:23.380
Companies are desperate to find talent.

00:19:23.711 --> 00:19:26.800
If we can successfully train
people with disabilities

00:19:26.801 --> 00:19:30.790
in these in-demand skills,
we are not doing charity.

00:19:30.911 --> 00:19:37.151
We are meeting market demand
while simultaneously advancing inclusion.

00:19:39.431 --> 00:19:44.441
Secondly, this access
fosters greater independence.

00:19:44.860 --> 00:19:48.879
Economic empowerment
through employment leads directly

00:19:48.880 --> 00:19:51.430
to financial and social independence,

00:19:51.941 --> 00:19:55.210
allowing individuals
to control their own futures

00:19:55.480 --> 00:19:58.300
and participate more actively
in the economy.

00:19:59.590 --> 00:20:01.240
Independence is dignity,

00:20:01.690 --> 00:20:07.179
is the ability to make your own choices,
support yourself and potentially

00:20:07.180 --> 00:20:10.840
your family, and live life
on your own terms.

00:20:11.231 --> 00:20:15.219
When people with disabilities
are systematically excluded

00:20:15.220 --> 00:20:20.051
from economic opportunities,
they often become dependent

00:20:20.080 --> 00:20:23.861
on family members,
social services, or charity.

00:20:24.491 --> 00:20:27.669
While support systems
are important, the ability

00:20:27.670 --> 00:20:31.001
to be economically self-sufficient
is transformative.

00:20:31.600 --> 00:20:35.440
